data.description: Woah Stop the Car! Location! Location! Location! Finished Backyard - Low maintenance with high-quality artificial turf and elegant pavers. Owner's Suite - Experience luxury in a spacious suite, complete with a separate soaking tub & shower.  Infused Air Freshener & Humidifier-Installed directly in the HVAC system for optimal comfort throughout. This community offers a blend of relaxation, fun, and convenience. Community pool, 24-gym, Sports Courts, BBQ & Ramada spaces, many gathering areas with fire pits, & reservable club house. Special Military Veterans Deal! Ask about our assumable option with a super low rate of 2.25% for a portion of the loan. Vet buyers must finance the remaining of the loan. Substitution of entitlement available for those who qualify!
